Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with temporal logic and its translation to automata.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses synthesis of reactive systems from LTL specifications.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with automata and their determinization.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is possible as the paper discusses winning strategies for games.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also possible as the paper discusses tool implementations and practical applicability.
